&lt;h3&gt;🧡&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;About Alma&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;At Alma, we believe sustainable commerce depends on fair, well‑balanced trade. Because finance plays a pivotal role in business, our mission is to put it back in its rightful place - serving merchants and consumers.&amp;nbsp;Our installment and deferred payment solutions help merchants boost sales by 20% or more, increase customer loyalty, and deliver a seamless shopping experience - without encouraging bad debt.&amp;nbsp;As the buy now pay later leader in France and active in 10 European countries, we&#39;ve empowered over +25,000 merchants and 10 million consumers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;With 380+ Almakers and €100M+ ARR, Alma is scaling rapidly across Europe as a member of the Next40, and we&#39;re just getting started!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;👐&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;About the team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reporting to the Head of Sales, you will join a fast-moving Enterprise sales team focused on expanding Alma&#39;s footprint across Europe. Since our creation in 2018, we&#39;ve grown to 18,000+ merchants across 10 countries, and acquisition of new Enterprise accounts is at the heart of our next growth chapter.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This position is a CDI based in Paris.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;💼 &lt;strong&gt;About the job&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a &lt;strong&gt;Business Development Representative (BDR)&lt;/strong&gt;, your impact at Alma will be immediate and tangible. You will directly contribute to growing our Enterprise merchant portfolio and increasing payment volumes processed by Alma.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your main responsibilities:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive Enterprise prospecting&lt;/strong&gt; through cold outreach (phone, email, social networks, Sales Navigator) on a defined block of verticals targeting merchants with 250M€+ turnover, in close collaboration with the Growth and Marketing teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build and qualify a strong pipeline&lt;/strong&gt; by implementing a structured prospecting strategy, actively following up on targets, and identifying potential projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Generate high-quality qualified appointments&lt;/strong&gt; for your Enterprise Account Executives to accelerate deal closings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Track and optimize your activity&lt;/strong&gt; to continuously improve your prospecting methods and contribute to team best practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;🧰 &lt;strong&gt;You will work with&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Salesforce · Sales Navigator · Outreach/Salesloft · Greenhouse · Slack · Notion&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;🧩 &lt;strong&gt;About you&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;To succeed in this job&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have prior experience in a BDR, SDR, or similar role with a focus on &lt;strong&gt;Enterprise B2B sales&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are &lt;strong&gt;native or bilingual in French&lt;/strong&gt; and have full professional proficiency in English&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are &lt;strong&gt;ambitious, resilient and driven by challenge&lt;/strong&gt;: exceeding targets is what gets you out of bed in the morning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;And it will be nice if you also&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have knowledge of the &lt;strong&gt;FinTech, e-commerce or payments&lt;/strong&gt; ecosystem&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have experience selling &lt;strong&gt;B2B SaaS&lt;/strong&gt; solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are &lt;strong&gt;rigorous and structured&lt;/strong&gt; in your follow-up and reporting, with a methodical approach to pipeline management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
