&lt;h3 class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;👐 &lt;strong&gt;About the team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;You will join the Data Engineering team, which is moving closer to the Platform organization to strengthen collaboration with SRE and Software Engineering and improve SLA standards on the data platform.&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;You will report to Jonathan, Engineering Manager of the SRE team, and work within a broader data community of 3 Central Data Analysts, 2 Product Data Analysts, 6 Business Analysts, and a 5-person AI team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;This position is a permanent contract (CDI) based in Paris.&lt;/p&gt;
