&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;👐 About the team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;People Operations&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;team is the backbone of Alma&#39;s People function — keeping everything running smoothly from a new hire&#39;s first day to their last, and making sure our processes are compliant, efficient, and built to scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll report to Limthary, Head of People Ops, and work at the crossroads of HR administration, payroll, systems, and data. This is a senior IC role where you&#39;ll be a trusted go-to for employees and a key partner for cross-functional teams.&lt;/p&gt;
