&lt;li&gt;Handle all employee administrative documents throughout the lifecycle&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage visa applications and related administrative authorizations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee the administrative management of EoR employees&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track and update leave balances and manage absence-related topics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be the first point of contact for employee administrative requests&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in daily payroll activities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead &amp;amp; contribute to HR Projects&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
