&lt;li&gt;Maintain and improve process documentation and the People knowledge base&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively identify areas for improvement and drive continuous optimization of our processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the implementation of new tools and vendors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own HR Systems &amp;amp; People Data&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
